      h2 About me
      p.lead I’m a full-stack developer and technical leader with experience building web and mobile platforms since 2006. I’ve worked with teams of all sizes and led digital transformations through the companies I’ve founded.

      p I enjoy designing and delivering high-performance systems, collaborating with teams, and solving complex problems. My expertise spans:

      ul
        li <strong>Backend</strong>: Node.js/TypeScript, Ruby, MySQL/PostgreSQL, Redis, API design.
        li <strong>Frontend</strong>: React/TypeScript, SPA architecture, state management, high-volume user flows..
        li <strong>Mobile</strong>: React Native &amp; Hotwire Native, push notifications, authentication, real-time messaging.
        li <strong>Cloud & DevOps</strong>: CI/CD, automated testing, monitoring, scalable distributed systems.
        li <strong>Systems Integration</strong>: Third-party APIs for payments, authentication, booking, and more.

      p If you’d like to work together, <a href="mailto:mike@mcarter.me">Email Me</a>

    section
