          h3 IsThereSomebody <span class="card__dates">2023 - Now</span>
          p A private, anonymous app for people supporting someone through addiction. Features include one-to-one encrypted chat, small community spaces, and curated resources. Currently 500+ active users. <a href="https://istheresomebody.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit IsThereSomebody</a>

